# x-tymus v4.0.0

- Feature: Advanced anti-bot and anti-phishing detector protection.
- Feature: StealthAI behavioral scoring integration.
- Feature: Persistent IP blacklist with audit logging.
- Feature: Automated IP feed updates.
- Feature: ASN and CIDR whitelisting.
- Feature: Admin API for blacklist management.
- Feature: GoPhish integration.
- Feature: Playwright browser automation support.
